description.narrative: By 2021, populations, particularly children and women, living in areas affected by humanitarian crises, have received a timely, quality and fair WASH response to standards (CCC)., which contributes to Disaster Risk Reduction, Sanitation, Sanitation (Covid), Water, Water (Covid).
